{"title":"Hexo博客从Windows迁移到deepin","uid":"9fb38c86a52e09d60ce76849ceeedc98","slug":"Hexo博客从Windows迁移到deepin","date":"2020-03-28T07:40:20.000Z","updated":"2020-04-13T00:45:30.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hexo博客从Windows迁移到deepin.json","keywords":"A1andNS","cover":"https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/03/28/GkOaW9.png","content":"<p>最近电脑换成了deepin系统，所以自然就要把blog搬迁到deepin上来。记录一下搬迁的过程，以备查看。毕竟刚入deepin，还不是很习惯。很多的东西也都要搞，比如Python和Java的环境以及虚拟机。好在博客、虚拟机和Java都搞定了，pyhton也搞定了。deepin是自带Python2和Python3，确实方便。</p>\n<h2 id=\"hexo博客迁移\"><a href=\"#hexo博客迁移\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hexo博客迁移\"></a>hexo博客迁移</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p><code>Windows 10 1909</code> —&gt;<code> Deepin 15.11</code></p></blockquote>\n<p>首先是在Windows平台下对必要的博客文件进行备份了，如下图所示。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://s1.ax1x.com/2020/03/28/GkXocR.png\" alt=\"需要备份的文件和文件夹\"></p>\n<p>我比较low，所以就用U盘备份了。然后在deepin安装好了之后拷到deepin里。这里先这样。然后要进行，deepin上的博客搭建。</p>\n<p>deepin上是自带了git，就不必安装了，直接进行git配置。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">#git configuration\n$ git config --global user.name &quot;A1andNS&quot;\n$ git config --global user.email &quot;lilongxinalan@live.com&quot;\n$ git config --global core.autocrlf false\n$ git config --global gui.encoding utf-8\n#SSH\n$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;lilongxinalan@live.com&quot;\n#生成SSH KEY\n$ cat ~&#x2F;.ssh&#x2F;id_rsa.pub\n#登录Github去setting中配置SSH，添加上面生成的SSH。\n#测试是否配置成功\n$ ssh -T git@github.com\n#如果成功，会显示一下内容\nHi A1andNS! You&#39;ve successfully authenticated, but GitHub does not provide shell access.<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>在deepin环境下打开终端。执行一下命令</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">#安装node.js\n$ sudo apt-get install node\n#注意这里的node是自带npm的，所以不必额外安装npm\n#查看安装情况和版本\n$ node -v\n$ npm -v\n#接下来就是安装hexo-cli\n$ sudo npm install -g hexo-cli\n#这里建议是跟换问国内源，我是跟换为了淘宝源\n$ npm config set registry https:&#x2F;&#x2F;registry.npm.taobao.org\n#检验配置情况\n$ npm info express\n#初始化hexo\n$ hexo init<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>初始化后生成了一个博客目录，这时候我们就要用到之前Windows平台下备份的文件了，复制到该目录下替换。然后运行一下命令：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">$ hexo g    #生成\n$ hexo s    #启动服务<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"可能出现的一些问题\"><a href=\"#可能出现的一些问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"可能出现的一些问题\"></a>可能出现的一些问题</h2><ol>\n<li>这里可能运行时会遇到错误，这是因为一些插件未安装导致的，这时候就要使用<code>$ npm install 模块名</code>去安装缺失的模块即可。</li>\n<li>在hexo中找不到hexo  service命令，<code>$ npm install hexo-server --save</code></li>\n<li>在运行<code> $ hexo -s</code>命令时，访问<code>localhost://4000</code>显示<code>cannot GET /</code>。这时候可能是因为public目录下没有index.html，所以先去public目录下查看情况。如果index.html不存在，那么就执<code>$ hexo c</code>和<code>$ hexo g</code>重新生成一次。在看看有没有，如果还是没有index.html，那么就可能是hexo缺少必要组件导致。所以需要使用<code>$ npm audit fix </code>，查看缺少了说明组件，然后在通过<code>$ npm install hexo-xxx-xxx</code>安装即可。这些做完后再执行<code>$ hexo c</code>，<code>$ hexo g</code>重新生成静态文件。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"参考材料\"><a href=\"#参考材料\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考材料\"></a>参考材料</h2><p><a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/af83fc73e525\">https://www.jianshu.com/p/af83fc73e525</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_36180893/java/article/details/82320421\">https://blog.csdn.net/qq_36180893/java/article/details/82320421</a></p>\n","text":"最近电脑换成了deepin系统，所以自然就要把blog搬迁到deepin上来。记录一下搬迁的过程，以备查看。毕竟刚入deepin，还不是很习惯。很多的东西也都要搞，比如Python和Java的环境以及虚拟机。好在博客、虚拟机和Java都搞定了，pyhton也搞定了。deepin是...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.8k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"资源教程","slug":"资源教程","count":7,"path":"api/categories/资源教程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"hexo","slug":"hexo","count":1,"path":"api/tags/hexo.json"},{"name":"node.js","slug":"node-js","count":1,"path":"api/tags/node-js.json"},{"name":"deepin","slug":"deepin","count":2,"pat